  "abstract": "The Board is publishing for comment a staff commentary to Regulation C (Home Mortgage Disclosure). The commentary applies and interprets the requirements of Regulation C. The proposed commentary provides guidance on various issues including the treatment under Regulation C of prequalifications, participations, refinancings, home [[Page 30014]] equity lines, mergers, and loan applications received through a broker. The Board believes the proposed commentary will reduce burden and ease compliance ",
